    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "ordered_code_text",
      "x": 525,
      "y": 145,
      "width": 390,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Ordered target statistics:\n  \u03c3 = random permutation [x\u2083, x\u2081, x\u2087, x\u2082, ...]\n  \n  For x\u2087 (3rd in \u03c3):\n  TS(x\u2087) = [\u03a3y\u2c7c for j before x\u2087 + prior] / (count+1)\n  \n\u2713 Only uses PRECEDING samples \u2192 no leakage",
      "originalText": "Ordered target statistics:\n  \u03c3 = random permutation [x\u2083, x\u2081, x\u2087, x\u2082, ...]\n  \n  For x\u2087 (3rd in \u03c3):\n  TS(x\u2087) = [\u03a3y\u2c7c for j before x\u2087 + prior] / (count+1)\n  \n\u2713 Only uses PRECEDING samples \u2192 no leakage",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 40052,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 40053,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": null,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": "ordered_code",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
